<main>
  <section class="introduction">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>Hello! My name is Charles David Wilmot II, but you can call me Charlie.
      I have a diverse range of interests spanning real estate, space exploration,
      volleyball, piano, fishing, machine learning, AI, systems engineering, and
      computer science and engineering. I am passionate about solving complex problems and
      constantly seeking out new challenges.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- New Section: Undergraduate Research -->
  <section class="undergraduate-research">
    <h2>Undergraduate Research Recognition</h2>
    <%= image_tag 'charliesImages/bannerPhoto.jpeg', alt: 'Charlie in the Downtown Banner Campaign', class: 'feature-image small-image' %>
    <p>I was recently selected for the downtown banner campaign for my undergraduate research work. This has been a great honor and a testament to the hard work and dedication I have put into my studies and research activities.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- New Section: Volleyball -->
  <section class="volleyball">
    <h2>Volleyball</h2>
    <%= image_tag 'charliesImages/volleyballPhoto.JPG', alt: 'Charlie Fishing', class: 'feature-image small-image' %>
    <p>I have played Volleyball here all four years and am currently the president of the club.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- New Section: Fishing Hobby -->
  <section class="fishing-hobby">
    <h2>Fishing Adventures</h2>
    <div class="fishing-images">
      <%= image_tag 'charliesImages/fishPhoto.jpg', alt: 'Charlie Fishing', class: 'fishing-image' %>
      <%= image_tag 'charliesImages/fishPhoto2.jpeg', alt: 'Charlie Fishing', class: 'fishing-image' %>
      <%= image_tag 'charliesImages/fishPhoto3.jpeg', alt: 'Charlie Fishing', class: 'fishing-image' %>
    </div>
    <p>Fishing has always been a passion of mine. In this picture, I am proud to have caught a beautiful blue gill, a large bass, and mahi mahi.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- New Section: Work at Space Force -->
  <section class="space-force">
    <h2>Space Force Experience</h2>
    <div class="space-force-images">
      <%= image_tag 'charliesImages/spaceForce.PNG', alt: 'Charlie at Space Force', class: 'space-force-image' %>
      <%= image_tag 'charliesImages/spaceForce2.PNG', alt: 'Charlie at Space Force', class: 'space-force-image' %>
      <%= image_tag 'charliesImages/spaceForce3.PNG', alt: 'Charlie at Space Force', class: 'space-force-image' %>
    </div>
    <p>I had the unique opportunity to work at the Space Force, contributing to important missions and projects. I am excited to return and continue my career there after graduation.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- New Section: Eagle Scout -->
  <section class="eagle-scout">
    <h2>Eagle Scout</h2>
    <%= image_tag 'charliesImages/eagleScout.JPG', alt: 'Eagle Scout', class: 'feature-image small-image' %>
    <p>I earned the rank of Eagle Scout in 2019 and served as Senior Patrol Leader (SPL) my last year of Boy Scouts</p>
  </section>

  <!-- New Section: Eagle Scout -->
  <section class="space">
    <h2>Space</h2>
    <%= image_tag 'charliesImages/space.JPG', alt: 'Eagle Scout', class: 'feature-image small-image' %>
    <p>Every since I was a little kid, I have been infatuated with Space</p>
  </section>

  <section class="projects">
    <h2>My Projects</h2>
